></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yoPzxcQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SisterMidnight]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Catchy sappy story</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ABjYUUx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vDOFLRL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We met in Jr high and we’re good friends then dated, married and kids. Life was great even with the ups and downs. We have traveled the US, built great careers, even been successful porn stars(another story), been successful in life, everything looks great for us.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rqifBdV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>People have issues, and no one is perfect, but her whole life she has been battling her inner demons and we tackled them, counseling, therapy, meds have all been tried</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uNIGRni.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After 22 years together, 17 years married, and 2 great kids, she admitted defeat and can’t keep hurting me and lying to herself and needs to leave. I just lost my best friend, person I love, and my family (her family has always been there for me and still are, but won’t be the same) if you truly love someone you have to let them go. We have tried counseling in the past, she has been to so many counselors in the past and really tried, but breaks my heart that feelings are still there and it has to end.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MT9YUAo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Son came by and left me a crisis number hotline number to call. He has never seen his dad a mess, I’ve been the cool calm rational one. Now I’m a mess. Kids are keeping me going and strong, their mom and I are on good terms and working to make sure they know they are number one and that we are here too for them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e730HGh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Shameless plug, thanks everyone for keeping me going with your posts, stories, and memes. Feel free to reach out or whatever, new to having a account</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ABjYUUx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[spaceskull333]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>79 years old meets 3-D printer</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uXSDbEG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CutC3Q7.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uXSDbEG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vidadobl6]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When you have 30,000 wheels of cheese to turn</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/62TnUQk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/i2YOMGs.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>9 months is the minimum for Grana Padano but some wheels are aged a lot longer (they are classified as Riserva when they’re aged over 20 months)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qQLvmZy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://instagram.com/nyccheesechick?utm_medium=copy_link</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/62TnUQk</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ZUXUX]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Gwen from Total Drama Island</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VTuQlTq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7GhMmAe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Instagram.com/soot_sprite_o</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VTuQlTq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sootspriteo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sick burn, sickest when true. *ST:DISCO Spoilers ahead*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1io8x7